            <center><h1>Abstract</h1>
            <p>The "Online Online Crime File Management System" is an innovative web application developed using Java and MySQL, designed to enhance the efficiency and effectiveness of law enforcement agencies in handling crime-related data. The system caters to both users and administrators, streamlining the process of registering complaints, managing witnesses, tracking missing individuals, and handling crucial information about wanted criminals.</p> 

